Kuwait-China Refinery Construction to Start Next Year, Kuna Says

-- B y   F i o n a   M a c D o n a l d
-- 
2011-05-22T04:48:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-22/kuwait-china-refinery-construction-to-start-next-year-kuna-says.html
Kuwait Petroleum Corp. and  China
Petroleum & Chemical Corp. (600028)  will start the construction of a $9
billion refinery in  China  in the first quarter of next year,
state-run  Kuwait News Agency  reported, citing the Mayor of
Zhanjiang, Ruan Risheng.  China Petroleum will own 50 percent of the joint venture in
the  Guangdong province , while a Kuwait Petroleum-led group will
hold the rest.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fiona MacDonald in Kuwait at 
 fmacdonald4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  